    They never expire and are applied instantly.
  </p>

  <hr />

  <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap">

    <!-- Starter -->
    <div style="border:1px solid #ddd;padding:20px;border-radius:8px;flex:1">
